What this APK can & canâ€™t do
âœ… What it can do
Show a fake boot/loading screen
Look cool
Be shared with friends
Be used as a prank/demo
âŒ What Android will NOT allow
You cannot replace the real phone boot screen
You cannot run before Android starts
No app can do that without rooting
So this is a safe launcher-style loading screen, not a risky system mod.
